hadiths[114]{hadithnumber,text}:
4874,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bahut sey sahaba sey riwayat hai ke qasamat jahiliyat mein raaij thi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey isi tarah barqarar rakha jis tarah ye jahiliyat mein thi aur aap ney eik maqtool key barey mein qasamat ka faisla bhi kiya tha jis key qatl ka ilzam ansaar ney khaiber key yahudiyon par lagaya tha. Maamar ney in dono ki mukhalifat ki hai.
4875,"Hazrat ibne Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke qasamat jahiliyat mein thi, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey eik Ansari key barey mein barqarar rakha jo yahudiyon key eik kunwen mein maqtool paey gaey they. ansaar ney daawey kar diya tha ke yahudiyon ney hamarey aadmi ko qatl kiya hai."
4876,"Hazrat ibne Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke qasamat jahiliyat mein thi, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey eik Ansari key barey mein barqarar rakha jo yahudiyon key eik kunwen mein maqtool paey gaey they. ansaar ney daawey kar diya tha ke yahudiyon ney hamarey aadmi ko qatl kiya hai."
4877,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muhisa bhook aur mashaqqat key sataey huye Khaibar ki taraf gaey. Mahisa kisi kaam sey wapis aaye to unhein bataya gaya ke Abdullah bin Sahal ko qatl kar key kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. wo yahudiyon key paas gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum ney isey qatl kiya hai. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra wapis aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir ho kar puri baat aap sey zikr ki. phir wo khud, unkey badey bhai Huwesa aur (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal teeno aaye. Muhisa baat karney lagey kyonkey wo Khaibar mein (maqtool key sath) they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. tab Huwesa ney baat ki. phir Muhisa ney bhi baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat farmaya : ya to Yahudi tumharey maqtool ki diyat dengey ya unhein jang ladna hogi. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat yahudiyon ko khat likha. unhoney (jawaaban) likha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Huwesa, Muhisa aur Abdur-Rehman sey farmaya : kya tum (pachas) qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key badley key haq-daar bantey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi tumharey samney (pachas) qasmen kha lein? unhoney kaha : wo to musalman nahin (jhooti qasmen kha jaeyngey). tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us maqtool ki diyat apni taraf (baitul-maal) sey ada kar di aur in ko sau oontniyaan bhej dein. yahan tak ke unkey ghar mein dakhil ki gaeen. Hazrat Sahal ney farmaya : un mein sey eik surkh oontni ney mujhey laat bhi maari thi."
4878,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muhisa bhook aur mashaqqat key sataey huye Khaibar ki taraf gaey. Mahisa kisi kaam sey wapis aaye to unhein bataya gaya ke Abdullah bin Sahal ko qatl kar key kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. wo yahudiyon key paas gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum ney isey qatl kiya hai. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra wapis aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir ho kar puri baat aap sey zikr ki. phir wo khud, unkey badey bhai Huwesa aur (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal teeno aaye. Muhisa baat karney lagey kyonkey wo Khaibar mein (maqtool key sath) they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. tab Huwesa ney baat ki. phir Muhisa ney bhi baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat farmaya : ya to Yahudi tumharey maqtool ki diyat dengey ya unhein jang ladna hogi. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat yahudiyon ko khat likha. unhoney (jawaaban) likha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Huwesa, Muhisa aur Abdur-Rehman sey farmaya : kya tum (pachas) qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key badley key haq-daar bantey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi tumharey samney (pachas) qasmen kha lein? unhoney kaha : wo to musalman nahin (jhooti qasmen kha jaeyngey). tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us maqtool ki diyat apni taraf (baitul-maal) sey ada kar di aur in ko sau oontniyaan bhej dein. yahan tak ke unkey ghar mein dakhil ki gaeen. Hazrat Sahal ney farmaya : un mein sey eik surkh oontni ney mujhey laat bhi maari thi."
4879,"Hazrat Abu Lailaa bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) aur meri qom key buzurgon ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muhisa (Raziallahu anhu) faaqon key maarey huye khaibar ko gaey. Muhisa kaam sey wapis aaye to unhein bataya gaya ke Abdullah bin Sahal ko qatl kar key kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. wo yahudiyon key paas gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum ney isey qatl kiya hai. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamney isey qatl nahin kiya. wo Madina Munawra apni qom key paas aaye to sara waqia un sey bayan kiya. phir wo khud, unkey badey bhai Huwesa aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. Muheisa baat karney lagey kyonkey khaibar mein wohi they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. aap ka maqsad tha jo umr mein bada hai. Huwesa ney pehley baat ki. phir Muheisa ney bhi baat ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya to wo tumharey maqtool ki diyat dengey warna un sey aelan-e-jang kar diya jaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat un (yahudiyon) ko khat likha. unhoney jawab mein likha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Huwesa, Muheisa aur Abdur-Rehman sey farmaya : tum (pachas) qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon key haq-daar bantey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi tumharey samney qasmen uthaeyngey. unhoney kaha : wo to musalman nahin hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni taraf sey maqtool ki diyat ada farma di aur unkey paas sau oontniyaan bhej dein yahan tak ke wo unkey ghar mein dakhil ki gaeen. Hazrat Sahal ney kaha : un mein sey eik surkh oontni ney mujhey laat maari thi."
4880,"Hazrat Abu Lailaa bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) aur meri qom key buzurgon ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muhisa (Raziallahu anhu) faaqon key maarey huye khaibar ko gaey. Muhisa kaam sey wapis aaye to unhein bataya gaya ke Abdullah bin Sahal ko qatl kar key kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. wo yahudiyon key paas gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum ney isey qatl kiya hai. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamney isey qatl nahin kiya. wo Madina Munawra apni qom key paas aaye to sara waqia un sey bayan kiya. phir wo khud, unkey badey bhai Huwesa aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. Muheisa baat karney lagey kyonkey khaibar mein wohi they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. aap ka maqsad tha jo umr mein bada hai. Huwesa ney pehley baat ki. phir Muheisa ney bhi baat ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya to wo tumharey maqtool ki diyat dengey warna un sey aelan-e-jang kar diya jaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat un (yahudiyon) ko khat likha. unhoney jawab mein likha : Allah ki qism ! hamney usey qatl nahin kiya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Huwesa, Muheisa aur Abdur-Rehman sey farmaya : tum (pachas) qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon key haq-daar bantey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi tumharey samney qasmen uthaeyngey. unhoney kaha : wo to musalman nahin hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni taraf sey maqtool ki diyat ada farma di aur unkey paas sau oontniyaan bhej dein yahan tak ke wo unkey ghar mein dakhil ki gaeen. Hazrat Sahal ney kaha : un mein sey eik surkh oontni ney mujhey laat maari thi."
4881,"Hazrat Sahal ibne Abi Hasma aur Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hazraat Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) safar ko nikley yahan tak ke jab wo khaibar pahunchey to wahan apney apney kaam mein alag alag ho gaey. phir achcha Muheisa ney Abdullah bin Sahal ko maqtool paya. in ko dafn karney key baad wo khud, Huwesa bin Masood aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal, jo ke sab sey chhotey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman (maqtool ka bhai honey key natey) apney dono sathiyon sey pehley baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : umr key lihaz sey badey ko pehley baat karney do. wo chup ho gaey aur deegar do sathiyon ney baaten kin. phir us ney bhi unkey sath sath baaten kin. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney Abdullah bin Sahal key qatl ka maamla pesh kiya. aap ney un sey farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon key (badley) ya qatil key mustahiq bantey ho? unhoney kaha : hum kaisey qism khaeyn jab ke hum to moqey par hazir nahin they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen utha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : hum kafiron ki qasmen kis tarah qubul kar len? jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye soorate-hal dekhi to aap ney (apni taraf sey) maqtool ki diyat dey di."
4882,"Hazrat Sahal ibne Abi Hasma aur Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hazraat Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) safar ko nikley yahan tak ke jab wo khaibar pahunchey to wahan apney apney kaam mein alag alag ho gaey. phir achcha Muheisa ney Abdullah bin Sahal ko maqtool paya. in ko dafn karney key baad wo khud, Huwesa bin Masood aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal, jo ke sab sey chhotey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman (maqtool ka bhai honey key natey) apney dono sathiyon sey pehley baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : umr key lihaz sey badey ko pehley baat karney do. wo chup ho gaey aur deegar do sathiyon ney baaten kin. phir us ney bhi unkey sath sath baaten kin. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney Abdullah bin Sahal key qatl ka maamla pesh kiya. aap ney un sey farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon key (badley) ya qatil key mustahiq bantey ho? unhoney kaha : hum kaisey qism khaeyn jab ke hum to moqey par hazir nahin they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen utha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : hum kafiron ki qasmen kis tarah qubul kar len? jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye soorate-hal dekhi to aap ney (apni taraf sey) maqtool ki diyat dey di."
4883,Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma aur Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Muheisa bin Masood aur Abdullah bin Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) apney kisi kaam sey khaibar gaey aur khajuron key darakhton mein alag alag ho gaey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Sahal qatl kar diye gaey. unka bhai Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal aur uskey chacha zaad bhai Huwesa aur Muheisa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman ney apney bhai key barey mein baat shuru ki jabkey wo un teeno mein sey chhotey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat kerni chahiye. phir un do bhaiyon ney apney maqtool key barey mein baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey pachas aadmi qasmen uthaeyn. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum to moqey par mojud nahin they. hum kaisey qasmen uthaeyn? aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen dey kar tum sey bari ho jaeyngey. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kafir log hain. (un ki qasmon ka kya aetbar?) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni taraf sey maqtool ki diyat ada kar di. Hazrat Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main unkey oonton key baadey mein dakhil huwa to un oonton mein sey eik oontni ney mujhey laat maari.
4884,Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma aur Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Muheisa bin Masood aur Abdullah bin Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) apney kisi kaam sey khaibar gaey aur khajuron key darakhton mein alag alag ho gaey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Sahal qatl kar diye gaey. unka bhai Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal aur uskey chacha zaad bhai Huwesa aur Muheisa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman ney apney bhai key barey mein baat shuru ki jabkey wo un teeno mein sey chhotey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat kerni chahiye. phir un do bhaiyon ney apney maqtool key barey mein baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey pachas aadmi qasmen uthaeyn. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum to moqey par mojud nahin they. hum kaisey qasmen uthaeyn? aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen dey kar tum sey bari ho jaeyngey. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kafir log hain. (un ki qasmon ka kya aetbar?) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni taraf sey maqtool ki diyat ada kar di. Hazrat Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main unkey oonton key baadey mein dakhil huwa to un oonton mein sey eik oontni ney mujhey laat maari.
4885,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey. un dino (khaibar yahudiyon sey) suleh thi. wo apney apney kaam mein idhar-udhar ho gaey. phir Muheisa, Abdullah bin Sahal ki taraf aaye to wo apney khoon mein luthdey huye maqtool padey they. unhoney unhein dafn kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra aaye aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal, Huwesa aur Muheisa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman jo umr mein un sab sey chhotey they, baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. wo khamosh ho gaey aur dusrey do bhaiyon ney baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen utha kar apney maqtool key khoon key haq-daar bantey ho? wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn jabkey hum to moqaey par mojud hi na they aur na hamney kisi ko dekha hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar tum sey bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon sey kaisey qasmen uthwaaen? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool ki diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di."
4886,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey. un dino (khaibar yahudiyon sey) suleh thi. wo apney apney kaam mein idhar-udhar ho gaey. phir Muheisa, Abdullah bin Sahal ki taraf aaye to wo apney khoon mein luthdey huye maqtool padey they. unhoney unhein dafn kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra aaye aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal, Huwesa aur Muheisa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman jo umr mein un sab sey chhotey they, baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. wo khamosh ho gaey aur dusrey do bhaiyon ney baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen utha kar apney maqtool key khoon key haq-daar bantey ho? wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn jabkey hum to moqaey par mojud hi na they aur na hamney kisi ko dekha hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar tum sey bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon sey kaisey qasmen uthwaaen? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool ki diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di."
4887,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood bin Zaid khaibar gaey. aur un dino (khaibar ke Yahud sey) suleh thi. wo apney apney kaam mein alag ho gaey. phir Muheisa, Abdullah bin Sahal ki taraf aaye to unhein khoon mein lat-pat paya. khair ! unhoney unhein dafn kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra pahunchey aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal aur apney bhai Huwesa bin Masood ko ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman jo sab sey chhotey they, baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. wo chup ho gaey. dusrey do hazraat ney baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney sathi ya qatil key haq daar bantey ho? wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn jab ke hum moqey par mojud nahin they aur na hamney kisi (qatil) ko dekha hai? aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon ki qasmen kaisey qubul keren? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di."
4888,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal aur Muheisa bin Masood bin Zaid khaibar gaey. aur un dino (khaibar ke Yahud sey) suleh thi. wo apney apney kaam mein alag ho gaey. phir Muheisa, Abdullah bin Sahal ki taraf aaye to unhein khoon mein lat-pat paya. khair ! unhoney unhein dafn kiya. phir wo Madina Munawra pahunchey aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal aur apney bhai Huwesa bin Masood ko ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman jo sab sey chhotey they, baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. wo chup ho gaey. dusrey do hazraat ney baat cheet ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney sathi ya qatil key haq daar bantey ho? wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn jab ke hum moqey par mojud nahin they aur na hamney kisi (qatil) ko dekha hai? aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon ki qasmen kaisey qubul keren? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di."
4889,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari aur Muheisa bin Masood dono khaibar gaey. wahan wo apney apney kaam mein idhar-udhar ho gaey to Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari qatl kar diye gaey. phir Muheisa, maqtool ka bhai Abdur-Rehman aur Huwesa bin Masood Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman baat shuru karney lagey to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. to Muheisa aur Huwesa ney baat shuru ki aur Abdullah bin Sahal key qatl ka waqia bayan kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney qatil ka muaakhza (pakad) kar saktey ho? wo kehney lagey : hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn hum to wahan mojud nahin they aur na hamney waqia dekha hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon ki qasmen kaisey qubul karen ! phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat khud ada farma di. Hazrat Sahal ney farmaya : hamarey baadey mein un oonton mein sey eik oontni ney mujhey laat bhi maari thi."
4890,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari aur Muheisa bin Masood dono khaibar gaey. wahan wo apney apney kaam mein idhar-udhar ho gaey to Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari qatl kar diye gaey. phir Muheisa, maqtool ka bhai Abdur-Rehman aur Huwesa bin Masood Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Abdur-Rehman baat shuru karney lagey to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. to Muheisa aur Huwesa ney baat shuru ki aur Abdullah bin Sahal key qatl ka waqia bayan kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney qatil ka muaakhza (pakad) kar saktey ho? wo kehney lagey : hum kaisey qasmen khaeyn hum to wahan mojud nahin they aur na hamney waqia dekha hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir logon ki qasmen kaisey qubul karen ! phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat khud ada farma di. Hazrat Sahal ney farmaya : hamarey baadey mein un oonton mein sey eik oontni ney mujhey laat bhi maari thi."
4891,"Hazrat Sahal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Sahal maqtool paey gaey. unka bhai aur uskey do chacha zad bhai Huwesa aur Muheisa, aur wo dono Abdullah bin Sahal key bhi chacha zad bhai they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh huye. (unka bhai) Abdur-Rehman baat karney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney Abdullah bin Sahal ko khaibar key eik kunwen mein maqtool paya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum kin par ilzam lagatey ho? unhoney kaha : hum yahudiyon par ilzam lagatey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum pachas qasmen khatey ho ke yahudiyon ney usey qatl kiya hai? wo kehney lagey : hum aisi chiz ki qism kaisey kha saktey hain jo hamney nahin dekhi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar ke hamney usey qatl nahin kiya, bari ho jaeyngey. wo kehney lagey : hum un mushrikon ki qasmen kaisey taslim kar lein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di. Malik bin Anas ney ye riwayat mursal bayan ki hai."
4892,"Hazrat Sahal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Sahal maqtool paey gaey. unka bhai aur uskey do chacha zad bhai Huwesa aur Muheisa, aur wo dono Abdullah bin Sahal key bhi chacha zad bhai they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh huye. (unka bhai) Abdur-Rehman baat karney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney Abdullah bin Sahal ko khaibar key eik kunwen mein maqtool paya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum kin par ilzam lagatey ho? unhoney kaha : hum yahudiyon par ilzam lagatey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum pachas qasmen khatey ho ke yahudiyon ney usey qatl kiya hai? wo kehney lagey : hum aisi chiz ki qism kaisey kha saktey hain jo hamney nahin dekhi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar ke hamney usey qatl nahin kiya, bari ho jaeyngey. wo kehney lagey : hum un mushrikon ki qasmen kaisey taslim kar lein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat apni taraf sey ada farma di. Malik bin Anas ney ye riwayat mursal bayan ki hai."
4893,Hazrat Bashir bin Yasar ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey aur apney apney kamon mein idhar-udhar ho gaey to Abdullah bin Sahal qatl kar diye gaey. Muheisa Madina Munawra aaye aur apney bhai Huwesa aur (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal samet Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye (maqtool Abdullah key) bhai honey ki wajeh sey Abdur-Rehman baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. phir Huwesa aur Muheisa ney aap sey baat cheet ki aur Abdullah bin Sahal ka masla pesh kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon ya apney qatil key mustahiq bantey ho. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha : Bashir bin Yasar ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney paas (baitul-mal) sey diyat ada farma di. Saeed bin Ubaid Al Taai ney un (Bashir bin Yasar sey riwayat karney walon) ki mukhalifat ki hai.
4894,Hazrat Bashir bin Yasar ney bataya ke Abdullah bin Sahal Ansari aur Muheisa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey aur apney apney kamon mein idhar-udhar ho gaey to Abdullah bin Sahal qatl kar diye gaey. Muheisa Madina Munawra aaye aur apney bhai Huwesa aur (maqtool key bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Sahal samet Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye (maqtool Abdullah key) bhai honey ki wajeh sey Abdur-Rehman baat karney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko pehley baat karney do. phir Huwesa aur Muheisa ney aap sey baat cheet ki aur Abdullah bin Sahal ka masla pesh kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : tum pachas qasmen kha kar apney maqtool key khoon ya apney qatil key mustahiq bantey ho. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha : Bashir bin Yasar ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney paas (baitul-mal) sey diyat ada farma di. Saeed bin Ubaid Al Taai ney un (Bashir bin Yasar sey riwayat karney walon) ki mukhalifat ki hai.
4895,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke meri qom key kuchh aadmi khaibar gaey. wahan wo alag alag ho gaey. unhoney apney mein sey eik shakhs ko maqtool paya to un logon sey, jinkey paas uski laash pai gaee thi, kaha : tum ney hamarey aadmi ko qatl kiya hai? unhoney kaha : hamney usey qatl nahin kiya aur na hum uskey qatil ko jantey hain. phir wo Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! hum khaibar gaey they. wahan hamney apney eik aadmi ko maqtool paya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. aap ney un sey farmaya : tum apney maqtool key qatil key barey mein gawah pesh karo. wo kehney lagey : hamarey paas to koi gawah nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir wo tumharey samney qasmen khaeyngey (aur bari ho jaeyngey). wo kehney lagey : hum to yahudiyon ki qism ka aetbar nahin kartey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pasand na farmaya ke us ka khoon bila-moawza rahey, lihaza aap ney sadqey key oonton mein sey sau oont diyat key taur par dey diye. Amr bin Shuaib ney in (hadees bayan karney waley baqi tamam riwayaton) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
4896,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke meri qom key kuchh aadmi khaibar gaey. wahan wo alag alag ho gaey. unhoney apney mein sey eik shakhs ko maqtool paya to un logon sey, jinkey paas uski laash pai gaee thi, kaha : tum ney hamarey aadmi ko qatl kiya hai? unhoney kaha : hamney usey qatl nahin kiya aur na hum uskey qatil ko jantey hain. phir wo Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! hum khaibar gaey they. wahan hamney apney eik aadmi ko maqtool paya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey ko baat karney do. aap ney un sey farmaya : tum apney maqtool key qatil key barey mein gawah pesh karo. wo kehney lagey : hamarey paas to koi gawah nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir wo tumharey samney qasmen khaeyngey (aur bari ho jaeyngey). wo kehney lagey : hum to yahudiyon ki qism ka aetbar nahin kartey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pasand na farmaya ke us ka khoon bila-moawza rahey, lihaza aap ney sadqey key oonton mein sey sau oont diyat key taur par dey diye. Amr bin Shuaib ney in (hadees bayan karney waley baqi tamam riwayaton) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
4897,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Muheisa ka chhota beta khaibar key darwazon par maqtool paya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey qatil key do aankho dekhey gawah lao, main usey uski rassi samet (giraftar kar key) terey supurd kar dunga. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! main do gawah kahan sey laun? wo to un yahudiyon key darwazon key samney maara gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : achchha to qasamat ki pachas (qasmen) kha ley. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main us baat par kis tarah qasmen khaaun jo main janta nahin? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir tum un sey qasamat ki pachas qasmen ley lo. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum un sey kaisey qasmen lein, wo to Yahudi hain (jhootey mashhoor hain)? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat yahudiyon par taqseem kar di aur nisf (aadhi) diyat mein aap ney un sey taawun farmaya."
4898,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Muheisa ka chhota beta khaibar key darwazon par maqtool paya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey qatil key do aankho dekhey gawah lao, main usey uski rassi samet (giraftar kar key) terey supurd kar dunga. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! main do gawah kahan sey laun? wo to un yahudiyon key darwazon key samney maara gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : achchha to qasamat ki pachas (qasmen) kha ley. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main us baat par kis tarah qasmen khaaun jo main janta nahin? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir tum un sey qasamat ki pachas qasmen ley lo. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum un sey kaisey qasmen lein, wo to Yahudi hain (jhootey mashhoor hain)? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat yahudiyon par taqseem kar di aur nisf (aadhi) diyat mein aap ney un sey taawun farmaya."
4899,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman aadmi ka khoon bahana jayez nahin, albatta teen jurmon mein usey qatl kiya ja sakta hai is ney kisi ko maar diya ho to usey uskey badley mein qatl kiya jaeyga ya shaadi shuda shakhs zina karey ya jo shakhs deene-Islam chhod kar musalmanon ki jamaat sey alag ho jaey."
4900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman aadmi ka khoon bahana jayez nahin, albatta teen jurmon mein usey qatl kiya ja sakta hai is ney kisi ko maar diya ho to usey uskey badley mein qatl kiya jaeyga ya shaadi shuda shakhs zina karey ya jo shakhs deene-Islam chhod kar musalmanon ki jamaat sey alag ho jaey."
4901,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik aadmi qatl ho gaya. qatil ko pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya. aap ney usey maqtool key waris key supurd kar diya. qatil kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mera irada usey qatl karney ka nahin tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool key waris sey farmaya : agar ye sachcha huwa aur tu ney isey qatl kar diya to to aag mein jaeyga. us ney usey chhod diya. wo qatil chamdey ki rassi sey bandhaa huwa tha. wo isi tarah apni rassi ko ghaseet'taa huwa nikla to us ka naam hi tundi ya rassi wala pad gaya."
4902,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik aadmi qatl ho gaya. qatil ko pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya. aap ney usey maqtool key waris key supurd kar diya. qatil kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mera irada usey qatl karney ka nahin tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool key waris sey farmaya : agar ye sachcha huwa aur tu ney isey qatl kar diya to to aag mein jaeyga. us ney usey chhod diya. wo qatil chamdey ki rassi sey bandhaa huwa tha. wo isi tarah apni rassi ko ghaseet'taa huwa nikla to us ka naam hi tundi ya rassi wala pad gaya."
4903,"Hazrat Waeyl Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke qatil ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pesh kiya gaya. usey maqtool ka waris ley kar aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : kya to isey maaf karta hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : jao. jab wo chal pada to aap ney usey bulaya aur farmaya : kya to maaf karta hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir to qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. farmaya : jao. jab wo chal pada to aap ney farmaya : agar to isey maaf kar dey to wo terey aur terey maqtool key gunah ka zimme-daar hoga. us ney usey maaf kar diya aur chhod diya. mainey qatil ko dekha, wo apni tundi ya rassi ko ghaseet'taa huwa ja raha tha."
4904,"Hazrat Waeyl Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke qatil ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pesh kiya gaya. usey maqtool ka waris ley kar aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : kya to isey maaf karta hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : jao. jab wo chal pada to aap ney usey bulaya aur farmaya : kya to maaf karta hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir to qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. farmaya : jao. jab wo chal pada to aap ney farmaya : agar to isey maaf kar dey to wo terey aur terey maqtool key gunah ka zimme-daar hoga. us ney usey maaf kar diya aur chhod diya. mainey qatil ko dekha, wo apni tundi ya rassi ko ghaseet'taa huwa ja raha tha."
4905,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main moqe par mojud tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik qatil laya gaya jisey maqtool ka wali eik tundi (chamdey ki rassi) key sath kheenchey la raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool key wali sey farmaya : kya to maaf kerega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya to diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : ja ley ja. jab wo us ko ley janey key liye aap key paas sey muda to aap ney us ko bulaya aur farmaya : kya to maaf kerega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. to aap ney farmaya : isey ley ja. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno ! agar to isey maaf kar dey to ye apney aur terey maqtool key gunahon ka bojh uthaeyga. us ney usey maaf kar key chhod diya. mainey usey dekha ke wo (qatil) apni tundi ko ghaseet'tey huye ja raha tha."
4906,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main moqe par mojud tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik qatil laya gaya jisey maqtool ka wali eik tundi (chamdey ki rassi) key sath kheenchey la raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool key wali sey farmaya : kya to maaf kerega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya to diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : ja ley ja. jab wo us ko ley janey key liye aap key paas sey muda to aap ney us ko bulaya aur farmaya : kya to maaf kerega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya diyat lega? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir qatl kerega? us ney kaha : haan. to aap ney farmaya : isey ley ja. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno ! agar to isey maaf kar dey to ye apney aur terey maqtool key gunahon ka bojh uthaeyga. us ney usey maaf kar key chhod diya. mainey usey dekha ke wo (qatil) apni tundi ko ghaseet'tey huye ja raha tha."
4907,eik aur sanad sey Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us jaisi riwayat bayan kartey hain. Yahya ney kaha : ye riwayat us (sabiqa (pichhli) riwayat ) sey (sanad se) achchhi hai.
4908,eik aur sanad sey Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us jaisi riwayat bayan kartey hain. Yahya ney kaha : ye riwayat us (sabiqa (pichhli) riwayat ) sey (sanad se) achchhi hai.
4909,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik shakhs aaya jiski gardan mein rassi thi (matlab ye ke eik shakhs dusrey aadmi ko galey mein tundi dal kar laya). aur (wohi laney wala shakhs) kehney laga : ye aur mera bhai eik kunwaan khod rahey they ke us ney kudaal uthai aur merey bhai key sar par dey maari aur usey maar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney inkar kar diya. aur phir kehney laga : aey Allah key Nabi ! ye aur mera bhai eik kunwen mein khudaai kar rahey they to isney kudaal utha kar apney sathi key sar par dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. aap ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney phir inkar kiya. kuchh der baad phir utha aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye aur mera bhai dono eik kunwen ki khudaai kar rahey they. us ney kudaal uthai aur apney sathi key sar par maar di aur uski jaan nikal di. aap ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney phir inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : phir ja (lekin yad rakh ke) agar tu ney isey qatl kar diya to to bhi is jaisa hi hoga. wo usey ley kar chala gaya yahan tak ke kafi door nikal gaya. to hamney usey aawaz di ke to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baat nahin sunta? wo wapis aaya aur kehney laga : agar mainey isey qatl kar diya to is jaisa ho jaunga? aap ney farmaya : han, isey maaf kar dey. phir (us ney qatil ko chhod diya to) qatil apni tundi samet nikal bhaagaa yahan tak ke hamari nigahon sey ojhal ho gaya."
4910,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik shakhs aaya jiski gardan mein rassi thi (matlab ye ke eik shakhs dusrey aadmi ko galey mein tundi dal kar laya). aur (wohi laney wala shakhs) kehney laga : ye aur mera bhai eik kunwaan khod rahey they ke us ney kudaal uthai aur merey bhai key sar par dey maari aur usey maar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney inkar kar diya. aur phir kehney laga : aey Allah key Nabi ! ye aur mera bhai eik kunwen mein khudaai kar rahey they to isney kudaal utha kar apney sathi key sar par dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. aap ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney phir inkar kiya. kuchh der baad phir utha aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye aur mera bhai dono eik kunwen ki khudaai kar rahey they. us ney kudaal uthai aur apney sathi key sar par maar di aur uski jaan nikal di. aap ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney phir inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : phir ja (lekin yad rakh ke) agar tu ney isey qatl kar diya to to bhi is jaisa hi hoga. wo usey ley kar chala gaya yahan tak ke kafi door nikal gaya. to hamney usey aawaz di ke to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baat nahin sunta? wo wapis aaya aur kehney laga : agar mainey isey qatl kar diya to is jaisa ho jaunga? aap ney farmaya : han, isey maaf kar dey. phir (us ney qatil ko chhod diya to) qatil apni tundi samet nikal bhaagaa yahan tak ke hamari nigahon sey ojhal ho gaya."
4911,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik aadmi eik dusrey aadmi ko tundi (chamdey ki rassi) key sath kheenchtaa huwa aaya aur kehney laga : Allah key Rasool ! is ney merey bhai ko qatl kar diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us (dusrey aadmi) sey puchha : kya tu ney usey qatl kiya hai? pehla aadmi kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar ye na maaney to main gawah pesh karunga. dusrey aadmi ney kaha : han, mainey usey qatl kiya hai. aap ney farmaya : kaisey qatl kiya? us ney kaha : main aur wo eik darkht sey endhan key liye lakdiyan kaat rahey they. us ney mujhey gaali dey kar ghussa dila diya to mainey kulhaada uskey sar ki choti par dey maara. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya terey paas itna maal hai jo to apni jaan bachaney key liye ada kerey? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas to merey kulhaadey aur meri chadar key siwa kuchh nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya khayal hai teri qom tujhey kharid leygi? (teri diyat dey kar tujhey bacha leygi?) us ney kaha : main apni qom key nazdik is sey kam martaba hun. aap ney uski rassi pehley aadmi ki taraf phenk di aur farmaya : lo apney qatil ko sambhalo. jab wo peeth pher kar chala to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar us ney usey qatl kar diya to ye bhi us jaisa hi hoga. log ja kar us aadmi ko miley aur kaha : tujh par afsos ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : agar us ney usey qatl kar diya to wo us jaisa hi hoga. wo aadmi wapis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey bataya gaya hai ke aap ney farmaya hai : agar us (main) ney isey qatl kar diya to ye bhi us jaisa hi hoga. halanke mainey to isey aap key farman sey pakda hai. aap ney farmaya : kya to nahin chahta ke ye shakhs tera aur terey maqtool ka gunah samet ley. (tumharey gunahon ki maafi ka sabab ban jaey?) us ney kaha : kyon nahin, phir kaha : agar ye baat hai to main maaf kar deta hun. aap ney farmaya : ye isi tarah hai jis tarah mainey kaha, yani wo terey aur terey maqtool key gunah uthaeyga."
4912,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik aadmi eik dusrey aadmi ko tundi (chamdey ki rassi) key sath kheenchtaa huwa aaya aur kehney laga : Allah key Rasool ! is ney merey bhai ko qatl kar diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us (dusrey aadmi) sey puchha : kya tu ney usey qatl kiya hai? pehla aadmi kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar ye na maaney to main gawah pesh karunga. dusrey aadmi ney kaha : han, mainey usey qatl kiya hai. aap ney farmaya : kaisey qatl kiya? us ney kaha : main aur wo eik darkht sey endhan key liye lakdiyan kaat rahey they. us ney mujhey gaali dey kar ghussa dila diya to mainey kulhaada uskey sar ki choti par dey maara. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya terey paas itna maal hai jo to apni jaan bachaney key liye ada kerey? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas to merey kulhaadey aur meri chadar key siwa kuchh nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya khayal hai teri qom tujhey kharid leygi? (teri diyat dey kar tujhey bacha leygi?) us ney kaha : main apni qom key nazdik is sey kam martaba hun. aap ney uski rassi pehley aadmi ki taraf phenk di aur farmaya : lo apney qatil ko sambhalo. jab wo peeth pher kar chala to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar us ney usey qatl kar diya to ye bhi us jaisa hi hoga. log ja kar us aadmi ko miley aur kaha : tujh par afsos ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : agar us ney usey qatl kar diya to wo us jaisa hi hoga. wo aadmi wapis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey bataya gaya hai ke aap ney farmaya hai : agar us (main) ney isey qatl kar diya to ye bhi us jaisa hi hoga. halanke mainey to isey aap key farman sey pakda hai. aap ney farmaya : kya to nahin chahta ke ye shakhs tera aur terey maqtool ka gunah samet ley. (tumharey gunahon ki maafi ka sabab ban jaey?) us ney kaha : kyon nahin, phir kaha : agar ye baat hai to main maaf kar deta hun. aap ney farmaya : ye isi tarah hai jis tarah mainey kaha, yani wo terey aur terey maqtool key gunah uthaeyga."
4913,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha tha ke eik aadmi eik dusrey shakhs ko kheenchtaa huwa laya, baqi riwayat mazkura riwayat key hum maana hai."
4914,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha tha ke eik aadmi eik dusrey shakhs ko kheenchtaa huwa laya, baqi riwayat mazkura riwayat key hum maana hai."
4915,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya tha. aap ney usey maqtool key wali key supurd farma diya ke (chahey to) qatl kar dey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney hum-nasheen (sathi) sey kaha : qatil, maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey. eik aadmi uskey peechhey gaya aur usey aap key farman ki khabar di. jab us ney us ko ye bataya to usney usey chhod diya. jab us ney chhoda to mainey dekha ke wo rassi ghaseet'tey huye bhaagaa ja raha tha. ( فَذَکَرْتُ ذٰلِکَ لِحَبِیْبٍ فَقَالَ … الخ ),mainey ye riwayat Habib sey bayan ki to usney kaha : mujh sey Saeed bin Ash'waa ney bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi ko maaf karney ka hukm diya."
4916,"Hazrat Waeyl (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya tha. aap ney usey maqtool key wali key supurd farma diya ke (chahey to) qatl kar dey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney hum-nasheen (sathi) sey kaha : qatil, maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey. eik aadmi uskey peechhey gaya aur usey aap key farman ki khabar di. jab us ney us ko ye bataya to usney usey chhod diya. jab us ney chhoda to mainey dekha ke wo rassi ghaseet'tey huye bhaagaa ja raha tha. ( فَذَکَرْتُ ذٰلِکَ لِحَبِیْبٍ فَقَالَ … الخ ),mainey ye riwayat Habib sey bayan ki to usney kaha : mujh sey Saeed bin Ash'waa ney bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi ko maaf karney ka hukm diya."
4917,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs apney rishte-daar key qatil ko pakad kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : diyat ley lo. us ney phir inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : ja phir isey qatl kar dey. to bhi is jaisa hi hai. wo usey ley gaya. peechhey sey koi aadmi usey ja kar mila aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : usey qatl kar dey to to bhi us jaisa hi hoga. to usney usey chhod diya. wo aadmi (qatil) merey paas sey guzra is haal mein ke wo rassi ghaseet'taa huwa bhaagaa ja raha tha.
4918,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs apney rishte-daar key qatil ko pakad kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey maaf kar dey. us ney inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : diyat ley lo. us ney phir inkar kiya. aap ney farmaya : ja phir isey qatl kar dey. to bhi is jaisa hi hai. wo usey ley gaya. peechhey sey koi aadmi usey ja kar mila aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : usey qatl kar dey to to bhi us jaisa hi hoga. to usney usey chhod diya. wo aadmi (qatil) merey paas sey guzra is haal mein ke wo rassi ghaseet'taa huwa bhaagaa ja raha tha.
4919,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : is aadmi ney merey bhai ko qatl kar dala hai. aap ney farmaya : ja isey qatl kar dey, jaisey us ney terey bhai ko qatl kiya hai. wo aadmi (qatil) kehney laga : Allah Taala sey daro aur mujhey maaf kar do. is sey tujhey bahut sawab milega. aur ye (maafi) terey aur terey bhai key liye qiyamat key din bahut achchhi sabit hogi. us ney isey chhod diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya gaya. aap ney qatil sey puchha to usney maqtool key waris sey jo kaha tha aap ko uski khabar di. to aap ney usey daantaa (aur farmaya : ) tera qatl ho jana is sulook sey behtar tha jo maqtool qiyamat key din tujh sey kerega. wo kahega : aey merey Rab is sey poochhiye ke is ney kis bina par mujhey qatl kiya tha?"
4920,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : is aadmi ney merey bhai ko qatl kar dala hai. aap ney farmaya : ja isey qatl kar dey, jaisey us ney terey bhai ko qatl kiya hai. wo aadmi (qatil) kehney laga : Allah Taala sey daro aur mujhey maaf kar do. is sey tujhey bahut sawab milega. aur ye (maafi) terey aur terey bhai key liye qiyamat key din bahut achchhi sabit hogi. us ney isey chhod diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya gaya. aap ney qatil sey puchha to usney maqtool key waris sey jo kaha tha aap ko uski khabar di. to aap ney usey daantaa (aur farmaya : ) tera qatl ho jana is sulook sey behtar tha jo maqtool qiyamat key din tujh sey kerega. wo kahega : aey merey Rab is sey poochhiye ke is ney kis bina par mujhey qatl kiya tha?"
4921,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Banu Qureza aur banu Nazeer (do Yahudi qabiley they.) banu Nazeer, Banu Qureza sey afzal shumar hotey they. agar Banu Qureza mein sey koi aadmi banu Nazeer key kisi aadmi ko qatl kar deta to usey qisas ke taur par qatl kar diya jata tha lekin jab banu Nazeer ka koi shakhs Banu Qureza key kisi aadmi ko qatl karta to wo sau wasq khajoor dey deta tha. jab Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mab-us huye Madina Munawra tashrif laye to banu Nazeer key eik aadmi ney Banu Qureza key eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya. Banu Qureza ney mutalba kiya ke qatil hamarey supurd karo taake hum usey qatl kar den. (unkey inkar par) Banu Qureza ney kaha : hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faisla farmaeyngey. wo aap key paas aaye to ye aayat utri : (وَ اِنْ حَکَمْتَ فَاحْکُمْ بَیْنَہُمْ بِالْقِسْطِ),''agar aap faisla farmaain to unkey darmiyan insaf key sath faisla farmaeyn.'' aur insaf yehi hai ke jaan key badley jaan (maqtool key badley qatil qatl kiya jaey). phir ye aayat utri : (اَفَحُکْمَ الْجَاہِلِیَّۃِ یَبْغُوْنَ),""kya ye ab bhi jahiliyat key faisley chahtey hain?''"
4922,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Banu Qureza aur banu Nazeer (do Yahudi qabiley they.) banu Nazeer, Banu Qureza sey afzal shumar hotey they. agar Banu Qureza mein sey koi aadmi banu Nazeer key kisi aadmi ko qatl kar deta to usey qisas ke taur par qatl kar diya jata tha lekin jab banu Nazeer ka koi shakhs Banu Qureza key kisi aadmi ko qatl karta to wo sau wasq khajoor dey deta tha. jab Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mab-us huye Madina Munawra tashrif laye to banu Nazeer key eik aadmi ney Banu Qureza key eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya. Banu Qureza ney mutalba kiya ke qatil hamarey supurd karo taake hum usey qatl kar den. (unkey inkar par) Banu Qureza ney kaha : hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faisla farmaeyngey. wo aap key paas aaye to ye aayat utri : (وَ اِنْ حَکَمْتَ فَاحْکُمْ بَیْنَہُمْ بِالْقِسْطِ),''agar aap faisla farmaain to unkey darmiyan insaf key sath faisla farmaeyn.'' aur insaf yehi hai ke jaan key badley jaan (maqtool key badley qatil qatl kiya jaey). phir ye aayat utri : (اَفَحُکْمَ الْجَاہِلِیَّۃِ یَبْغُوْنَ),""kya ye ab bhi jahiliyat key faisley chahtey hain?''"
4923,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Sura Maeyda ki aayaat jin mein Allah ney farmaya hai : (فَاحْکُمْ بَیْنَہُمْ اَوُ اَعْرِضُ عَنْھُمْ . . . . الْمُقْسِطِیْنَ),''aap un mein faisla karen ya na, (aap ki marzi hai) … insaf karney walon ko (hi pasand karta hai.)''ye aayaat banu Nazeer aur Banu Qureza key darmiyan diyat key jhagdey key barey mein nazil hui aur wo is tarah ke banu Nazeer key maqtooleen ko afzal khayal kiya jata tha, is liye un ki mukammal diyat (sau oont) ada ki jati thi jab ke Banu Qureza key maqtooleen ki nisf (aadhi) diyat ada ki jati thi. wo is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas faisla ley gaey to Allah Taala ney unkey barey mein ye aayaat nazil farmaee. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney in ko is barey mein haq ikhtiyar karney par majbur kiya aur aap ney sab ki diyat barabar qarar di."
4924,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Sura Maeyda ki aayaat jin mein Allah ney farmaya hai : (فَاحْکُمْ بَیْنَہُمْ اَوُ اَعْرِضُ عَنْھُمْ . . . . الْمُقْسِطِیْنَ),''aap un mein faisla karen ya na, (aap ki marzi hai) … insaf karney walon ko (hi pasand karta hai.)''ye aayaat banu Nazeer aur Banu Qureza key darmiyan diyat key jhagdey key barey mein nazil hui aur wo is tarah ke banu Nazeer key maqtooleen ko afzal khayal kiya jata tha, is liye un ki mukammal diyat (sau oont) ada ki jati thi jab ke Banu Qureza key maqtooleen ki nisf (aadhi) diyat ada ki jati thi. wo is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas faisla ley gaey to Allah Taala ney unkey barey mein ye aayaat nazil farmaee. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney in ko is barey mein haq ikhtiyar karney par majbur kiya aur aap ney sab ki diyat barabar qarar di."
4925,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad sey riwayat hai ke main aur Ashtar Nakhai Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. hamney kaha : kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko koi khususi wasiyat farmaee hai jo dusrey logon ko na farmaee ho? unhoney kaha : nahin, albatta meri us tehreer mein kuchh likha hai. phir unhoney apni talwaar ki miyaan sey wo tehreer nikali to is mein likha tha : tamam eman walon key khoon barabar hain. aur wo sab apney dushman key khilaf yakmusht hain. un mein sey kam martabey wala aam shakhs bhi kisi ko panah dey sakta hai. aagah raho ! kisi momin ko kafir key badley qatl na kiya jaey aur na kisi zimmi ko jab tak wo hamari panah mein hai. jo dushman bagawat kerega, usey us ka khamiyaza bhugatna padeyga. jo shakhs kisi baaghi ko panah mohaiyya kerey. is par Allah taalaa, farishton aur sab logon ki lanat hai."
4926,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad sey riwayat hai ke main aur Ashtar Nakhai Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. hamney kaha : kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko koi khususi wasiyat farmaee hai jo dusrey logon ko na farmaee ho? unhoney kaha : nahin, albatta meri us tehreer mein kuchh likha hai. phir unhoney apni talwaar ki miyaan sey wo tehreer nikali to is mein likha tha : tamam eman walon key khoon barabar hain. aur wo sab apney dushman key khilaf yakmusht hain. un mein sey kam martabey wala aam shakhs bhi kisi ko panah dey sakta hai. aagah raho ! kisi momin ko kafir key badley qatl na kiya jaey aur na kisi zimmi ko jab tak wo hamari panah mein hai. jo dushman bagawat kerega, usey us ka khamiyaza bhugatna padeyga. jo shakhs kisi baaghi ko panah mohaiyya kerey. is par Allah taalaa, farishton aur sab logon ki lanat hai."
4927,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tamam mominon key khoon barabar hain aur wo apney dushman kafiron key khilaf eik haath ki tarah hain. un mein sey aam shakhs bhi panah dey sakta hai. kisi momin ko kisi kafir key badley mein qatl nahin kiya ja sakta. na kisi zimmi ko qatl kiya ja sakta hai, jab tak us sey muahida qaaim hai."
4928,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tamam mominon key khoon barabar hain aur wo apney dushman kafiron key khilaf eik haath ki tarah hain. un mein sey aam shakhs bhi panah dey sakta hai. kisi momin ko kisi kafir key badley mein qatl nahin kiya ja sakta. na kisi zimmi ko qatl kiya ja sakta hai, jab tak us sey muahida qaaim hai."
4929,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey. jo shakhs apney ghulam ke naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uske naak, kaan kaat dengey aur jo apney ghulam ko khassi kerega, hum usey khassi kar dengey."
4930,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey. jo shakhs apney ghulam ke naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uske naak, kaan kaat dengey aur jo apney ghulam ko khassi kerega, hum usey khassi kar dengey."
4931,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey aur jo apney ghulam key naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uskey naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4932,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey aur jo apney ghulam key naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uskey naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4933,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kerengey aur jo shakhs apney ghulam ke naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uske naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4934,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kerengey aur jo shakhs apney ghulam ke naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uske naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4935,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney us (aurat ko aurat key badley qatl kerney) ki baabat logon sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla puchha to Hazrat Hamal bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur kaha : main do aurton key do kamron key darmiyan rehta tha ke eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi maar kar qatl kar diya, isi ke sath uskey pet ka bachcha bhi mar gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat main eik ghulam ya londi deney ka hukm diya aur us aurat key badley qatil aurat ko qatl karney ka hukm diya."
4936,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney us (aurat ko aurat key badley qatl kerney) ki baabat logon sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla puchha to Hazrat Hamal bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur kaha : main do aurton key do kamron key darmiyan rehta tha ke eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi maar kar qatl kar diya, isi ke sath uskey pet ka bachcha bhi mar gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat main eik ghulam ya londi deney ka hukm diya aur us aurat key badley qatil aurat ko qatl karney ka hukm diya."
4937,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki ko uski baaliyaan utaarney ki khatir qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us Yahudi ko us ladki key iwaz qatl kar diya.
4938,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki ko uski baaliyaan utaarney ki khatir qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us Yahudi ko us ladki key iwaz qatl kar diya.
4939,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki ki baaliyaan utaar lein. phir us ka sar do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya. logon ney ladki ko dekha to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. wo log uskey samney mukhtalif ashkhaas ka naam ley kar poochhney lagey : wo falan tha? wo falan tha? aakhir (us Yahudi key naam) par ladki ney haan ka ishara kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya to us Yahudi ka sar bhi isi tarah do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya gaya.
4940,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki ki baaliyaan utaar lein. phir us ka sar do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya. logon ney ladki ko dekha to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. wo log uskey samney mukhtalif ashkhaas ka naam ley kar poochhney lagey : wo falan tha? wo falan tha? aakhir (us Yahudi key naam) par ladki ney haan ka ishara kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya to us Yahudi ka sar bhi isi tarah do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya gaya.
4941,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik ladki ghar sey nikli. uskey kanon mein baaliyaan thin. eik Yahudi ney usey pakad liya us ka sar kuchla aur zewrat utaar kar ley gaya. jab us ladki ko dekha gaya to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to aap ney us sey puchha : tujhey kis ney maara hai? kya falan ney? us ney sar sey ishara kiya, nahin. farmaya : falan ney? yahan tak ke aap ney us Yahudi ka naam liya to us ney sar key isharay sey haan kaha. us Yahudi ko pakad laya gaya. aakhir us ney taslim kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya aur us ka sar bhi isi tarah do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya gaya."
4942,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik ladki ghar sey nikli. uskey kanon mein baaliyaan thin. eik Yahudi ney usey pakad liya us ka sar kuchla aur zewrat utaar kar ley gaya. jab us ladki ko dekha gaya to is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to aap ney us sey puchha : tujhey kis ney maara hai? kya falan ney? us ney sar sey ishara kiya, nahin. farmaya : falan ney? yahan tak ke aap ney us Yahudi ka naam liya to us ney sar key isharay sey haan kaha. us Yahudi ko pakad laya gaya. aakhir us ney taslim kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya aur us ka sar bhi isi tarah do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya gaya."
4943,Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman ko qatl karna jayez nahin siwaye iske ke wo in teen jaraaim mein sey koi jurm karey : shaadi shuda ho kar zina karey to usey rajm (sangsar) kiya jaeyga. kisi musalman shakhs ko jaan-boojh kar qatl kar dey. ya Islam sey khaarij ho jaey aur Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey jang shuru kar dey to usey qatl kiya jaeyga ya sooli par latkaayaa jaeyga ya apney ilaqey sey jala watan kar diya jaeyga.
4944,Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman ko qatl karna jayez nahin siwaye iske ke wo in teen jaraaim mein sey koi jurm karey : shaadi shuda ho kar zina karey to usey rajm (sangsar) kiya jaeyga. kisi musalman shakhs ko jaan-boojh kar qatl kar dey. ya Islam sey khaarij ho jaey aur Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey jang shuru kar dey to usey qatl kiya jaeyga ya sooli par latkaayaa jaeyga ya apney ilaqey sey jala watan kar diya jaeyga.
4945,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke hamney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap key paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki janib sey Quran Majeed key ilawa koi aur chiz bhi hai? unhoney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jisney daney ko phaad kar angoori nikali aur rooh ko paida farmaya ! nahin, magar ye ke Allah Taala kisi aadmi ko apni kitab ki samajh ata farmaey. (us mein farq ho sakta hai) ya phir is tehreer mein kuchh baaten hain. mainey kaha : is tehreer mein kya likha hai? unhoney farmaya : is mein diyat key masaayel hain. qaidi ko chhudaney ki fazilat ka bayan hai aur ye ke kisi musalman ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya jaeyga."
4946,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke hamney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap key paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki janib sey Quran Majeed key ilawa koi aur chiz bhi hai? unhoney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jisney daney ko phaad kar angoori nikali aur rooh ko paida farmaya ! nahin, magar ye ke Allah Taala kisi aadmi ko apni kitab ki samajh ata farmaey. (us mein farq ho sakta hai) ya phir is tehreer mein kuchh baaten hain. mainey kaha : is tehreer mein kya likha hai? unhoney farmaya : is mein diyat key masaayel hain. qaidi ko chhudaney ki fazilat ka bayan hai aur ye ke kisi musalman ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya jaeyga."
4947,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aam logon key ilawa mujhey koi khususi wasiyat nahin farmaee magar meri talwaar ki miyaan main eik tehreer hai. log aap sey israr kartey rahey (ke aap wo tehreer dikhayen) yahan tak ke aap ney wo tehreer nikali. is mein likha tha : tamam ehale-emaan key khoon barabar haisiyat rakhtey hain. eik aam momin bhi kisi shakhs ko tamam musalmanon ki taraf sey panah dey sakta hai. sab musalman kuffar key muqabley main eik haath ki tarah eik jaan hain. kisi musalman ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya ja sakta aur kisi zimmi ko uskey zimmi hotey huye qatl nahin kiya ja sakta.
4948,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aam logon key ilawa mujhey koi khususi wasiyat nahin farmaee magar meri talwaar ki miyaan main eik tehreer hai. log aap sey israr kartey rahey (ke aap wo tehreer dikhayen) yahan tak ke aap ney wo tehreer nikali. is mein likha tha : tamam ehale-emaan key khoon barabar haisiyat rakhtey hain. eik aam momin bhi kisi shakhs ko tamam musalmanon ki taraf sey panah dey sakta hai. sab musalman kuffar key muqabley main eik haath ki tarah eik jaan hain. kisi musalman ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya ja sakta aur kisi zimmi ko uskey zimmi hotey huye qatl nahin kiya ja sakta.
4949,Ashtar Nakhai sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke logon mein aisi baaten bahut pheli hui hain jo wo (idhar-udhar sey) suntey hain. agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko koi khususi ilm ya wasiyat ata farmaee hai to hamein bayan farmaeyn. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey koi khususi ilm ya wasiyat nahin farmaee jo dusrey logon ko ata na farmaee ho. albatta meri talwaar ki miyaan main eik tehreer mojud hai. dekha to is mein ye likha tha : tamam ehale-emaan key khoon barabar hain. eik aam musalman bhi sab musalmanon ki taraf sey panah dey sakta hai. kisi momin ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya ja sakta aur na kisi zimmi ko uskey zimmi hotey huye qatl kiya ja sakta hai. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
4950,Ashtar Nakhai sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke logon mein aisi baaten bahut pheli hui hain jo wo (idhar-udhar sey) suntey hain. agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko koi khususi ilm ya wasiyat ata farmaee hai to hamein bayan farmaeyn. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey koi khususi ilm ya wasiyat nahin farmaee jo dusrey logon ko ata na farmaee ho. albatta meri talwaar ki miyaan main eik tehreer mojud hai. dekha to is mein ye likha tha : tamam ehale-emaan key khoon barabar hain. eik aam musalman bhi sab musalmanon ki taraf sey panah dey sakta hai. kisi momin ko kisi kafir key badley qatl nahin kiya ja sakta aur na kisi zimmi ko uskey zimmi hotey huye qatl kiya ja sakta hai. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
4951,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zimmi ko nahaq qatl kerey. Allah Taala ney is par jannat haram farma di hai.
4952,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zimmi ko nahaq qatl kerey. Allah Taala ney is par jannat haram farma di hai.
4953,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi zimmi ko nahaq qatl kiya, Allah Taala ney is par jannat to eik taraf uski khushbu sughna tak haram kar diya hai."
4954,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi zimmi ko nahaq qatl kiya, Allah Taala ney is par jannat to eik taraf uski khushbu sughna tak haram kar diya hai."
4955,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey manqul hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zimmi ko qatl kerega wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyga halanke uski khushbu satar saal key fasley sey aati hai.
4956,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey manqul hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zimmi ko qatl kerega wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyga halanke uski khushbu satar saal key fasley sey aati hai.
4957,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi zimmi ko qatl kiya, wo jannat ki khushbu tak nahin pa sakeyga jabkey uski khushbu to chaalis saal key fasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
4958,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi zimmi ko qatl kiya, wo jannat ki khushbu tak nahin pa sakeyga jabkey uski khushbu to chaalis saal key fasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
4959,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke faqir logon key eik ghulam ney maaldaar logon key eik ghulam ka kaan kaat diya. wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to aap ney in ko koi moawza na dilaayaa.
4960,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke faqir logon key eik ghulam ney maaldaar logon key eik ghulam ka kaan kaat diya. wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to aap ney in ko koi moawza na dilaayaa.
4961,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney daant mein qisaas ka hukm jari farmaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka hukm qisaas hai.
4962,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney daant mein qisaas ka hukm jari farmaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka hukm qisaas hai.
4963,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey aur jo koi apney ghulam ki naak ya kaan kaat dey, hum uski naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4964,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, hum usey qatl kar dengey aur jo koi apney ghulam ki naak ya kaan kaat dey, hum uski naak, kaan kaat dengey."
4965,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko khassi kerey. hum usey khassi kar dengey aur jo apney ghulam ki naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uski naak, kaan kaatengey. ye alfaz ibne Bashaar key hain."
4966,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghulam ko khassi kerey. hum usey khassi kar dengey aur jo apney ghulam ki naak, kaan kaateyga, hum uski naak, kaan kaatengey. ye alfaz ibne Bashaar key hain."
4967,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rabeea ki behan Ummey Harisa ney eik insan ko zakhmi kar diya. wo ye muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qisaas dena hoga. Rabeea ki walida kehney lagin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! kya Ummey Harisa sey qisaas liya jaeyga? Allah ki qism ! hergiz nahin. us sey kabhi qisaas nahin liya jaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Subhan Allah ! Ummey Rabeea ! qisaas to Allah Taala ka hukm hai. wo kehney lagin, Allah ki qism ! nahin. us sey kabhi qisaas nahin liya jaeyga. wo isi tarah kehti rahin yahan tak ke doosre fariq ney diyat qubul kar li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key kuchh bandey aisey bhi hain jo Allah Taala key bharosey par qism kha lein to Allah Taala unhein sachcha kar deta hai."
4968,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rabeea ki behan Ummey Harisa ney eik insan ko zakhmi kar diya. wo ye muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qisaas dena hoga. Rabeea ki walida kehney lagin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! kya Ummey Harisa sey qisaas liya jaeyga? Allah ki qism ! hergiz nahin. us sey kabhi qisaas nahin liya jaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Subhan Allah ! Ummey Rabeea ! qisaas to Allah Taala ka hukm hai. wo kehney lagin, Allah ki qism ! nahin. us sey kabhi qisaas nahin liya jaeyga. wo isi tarah kehti rahin yahan tak ke doosre fariq ney diyat qubul kar li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key kuchh bandey aisey bhi hain jo Allah Taala key bharosey par qism kha lein to Allah Taala unhein sachcha kar deta hai."
4969,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri phuphi ney eik ladki ka samney wala daant tod diya. Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qisaas ka hukm dey diya. unkey bhai Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya us ka daant tod diya jaeyga ? nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko sachcha Nabi banaya hai ! us ka daant nahin toda jaeyga. is sey pehley unhoney us ladki key ghar walon sey maafi aur diyat ki guzarish ki thi (magar wo na maaney they). phir jab unkey bhai , jo Hazrat Anas key chacha they aur jange-uhad mein shaheed huye, ney qism kha li to wo log maafi par razi ho gaey. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key kuchh bandey aisey (buland martaba) hotey hain ke agar wo Allah Taala par bharosa kartey huye qism kha lein to Allah Taala un (ki qasam) ko sachcha kar deta hai."
4970,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri phuphi ney eik ladki ka samney wala daant tod diya. Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qisaas ka hukm dey diya. unkey bhai Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya us ka daant tod diya jaeyga ? nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko sachcha Nabi banaya hai ! us ka daant nahin toda jaeyga. is sey pehley unhoney us ladki key ghar walon sey maafi aur diyat ki guzarish ki thi (magar wo na maaney they). phir jab unkey bhai , jo Hazrat Anas key chacha they aur jange-uhad mein shaheed huye, ney qism kha li to wo log maafi par razi ho gaey. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key kuchh bandey aisey (buland martaba) hotey hain ke agar wo Allah Taala par bharosa kartey huye qism kha lein to Allah Taala un (ki qasam) ko sachcha kar deta hai."
4971,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (meri phuphi) Hazrat Rabeea (Raziallahu anha) ney eik ladki ka samney wala daant tod diya. unkey rishte-daaron ney ladki key rishte-daaron sey maafi maangi. unhoney inkar kar diya. unhein diyat ki pesh kaash! ki gaee to unhoney phir inkar kar diya. phir wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa gaey. aap ney qisaas ka hukm jari farma diya. Hazrat Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Rabeea ka daant toda jaeyga? nahin, qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya ! hergiz nahin toda jaeyga. aap ney farmaya : Anas ! Allah Taala ki Kitab to qisaas ka hukm deti hai. itney mein dusre fariq  razi ho gaye aur unhoney maafi dey di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala key kuchh bandey aisey hain ke agar Allah Taala ka naam ley kar qism kha lein to Allah Taala un ki laaj rakh leta hai."
4972,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (meri phuphi) Hazrat Rabeea (Raziallahu anha) ney eik ladki ka samney wala daant tod diya. unkey rishte-daaron ney ladki key rishte-daaron sey maafi maangi. unhoney inkar kar diya. unhein diyat ki pesh kaash! ki gaee to unhoney phir inkar kar diya. phir wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa gaey. aap ney qisaas ka hukm jari farma diya. Hazrat Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Rabeea ka daant toda jaeyga? nahin, qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya ! hergiz nahin toda jaeyga. aap ney farmaya : Anas ! Allah Taala ki Kitab to qisaas ka hukm deti hai. itney mein dusre fariq  razi ho gaye aur unhoney maafi dey di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala key kuchh bandey aisey hain ke agar Allah Taala ka naam ley kar qism kha lein to Allah Taala un ki laaj rakh leta hai."
4973,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key haath par kaat liya. us ney apna haath khincha to uskey samney wala eik daant ukhad gaya. us ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein uskey khilaf daawey daayer kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : to kya chahta hai? kya to chahta hai ke main usey kahun ke wo apna haath terey munh mein diye rakhey aur to usey chabaataa rahey, jaisey oont chabaataa hai? agar to chahta hai to apna haath uskey munh mein dal dey taake wo usey chabaaey. phir to chahey to apna haath khinch lena."
4974,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key haath par kaat liya. us ney apna haath khincha to uskey samney wala eik daant ukhad gaya. us ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein uskey khilaf daawey daayer kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : to kya chahta hai? kya to chahta hai ke main usey kahun ke wo apna haath terey munh mein diye rakhey aur to usey chabaataa rahey, jaisey oont chabaataa hai? agar to chahta hai to apna haath uskey munh mein dal dey taake wo usey chabaaey. phir to chahey to apna haath khinch lena."
4975,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey key bazu par kaat khaya. us ney apna bazu khincha to us (kaatney waley) ka samney wala daant gir gaya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein pesh kiya gaya. aap ney daant ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya balke farmaya : tera maqsad ye hai ke to oont ki tarah apney bhai ka gosht chabaataa rehta  (aur wo kuchh bhi na karta).
4976,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey key bazu par kaat khaya. us ney apna bazu khincha to us (kaatney waley) ka samney wala daant gir gaya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein pesh kiya gaya. aap ney daant ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya balke farmaya : tera maqsad ye hai ke to oont ki tarah apney bhai ka gosht chabaataa rehta  (aur wo kuchh bhi na karta).
4977,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik aadmi sey jhagda ho gaya to un mein sey eik ney dusrey ko daant kaataa. us ney uskey munh sey apna haath khincha to kaatney waley ka samney wala daant gir gaya. wo dono ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye to aap ney (ghussay sey) farmaya : kya tum mein sey eik aadmi apney bhai ko oont ki tarah chabaataa hai? jao is daant ki koi diyat nahin.
4978,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik aadmi sey jhagda ho gaya to un mein sey eik ney dusrey ko daant kaataa. us ney uskey munh sey apna haath khincha to kaatney waley ka samney wala daant gir gaya. wo dono ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye to aap ney (ghussay sey) farmaya : kya tum mein sey eik aadmi apney bhai ko oont ki tarah chabaataa hai? jao is daant ki koi diyat nahin.
4979,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) ney us aadmi key barey mein jisney dusrey ko kaataa tha jis sey us ka daant gir gaya tha, farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (us jaisey muqaddmey mein) farmaya tha : jao tujhey koi diyat nahin milegi."
4980,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) ney us aadmi key barey mein jisney dusrey ko kaataa tha jis sey us ka daant gir gaya tha, farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (us jaisey muqaddmey mein) farmaya tha : jao tujhey koi diyat nahin milegi."
4981,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key bazu par daant kaataa jis key natijey mein us ka samney wala daant ukhad gaya. wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur aap sey is ka tazkira kiya. aap ney farmaya : tera maqsad ye hai ke to apney bhai ka bazu oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta. phir aap ney is ka koi moawza na dilwaya.
4982,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi key bazu par daant kaataa jis key natijey mein us ka samney wala daant ukhad gaya. wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur aap sey is ka tazkira kiya. aap ney farmaya : tera maqsad ye hai ke to apney bhai ka bazu oont ki tarah chabaataa rehta. phir aap ney is ka koi moawza na dilwaya.
4983,"Hazrat Yaala ibne Munyah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main eik aadmi sey lad pada. hum mein sey eik ney dusrey ko daant kaataa to usney apna haath uskey munh sey khincha aur us ka daant ukhad diya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey eik aadmi apney bhai ko is tarah kaat'taa hai, jaisey oont? phir aap ney usey batil aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) qarar diya. (us key daant ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya.)"
4984,"Hazrat Yaala ibne Munyah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main eik aadmi sey lad pada. hum mein sey eik ney dusrey ko daant kaataa to usney apna haath uskey munh sey khincha aur us ka daant ukhad diya. ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey eik aadmi apney bhai ko is tarah kaat'taa hai, jaisey oont? phir aap ney usey batil aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) qarar diya. (us key daant ka koi moawza nahin dilwaya.)"
4985,"Hazrat Yaala ibn Muniyah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Tameem key eik aadmi ney eik dusrey shakhs sey ladaai ki aur uskey haath par daant gaad diye. us ney apna haath khincha to sath hi us ka daant bhi bahar aa gaya. wo ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey to aap ney farmaya : tum apney bhai ko is tarah kaat'tey ho jis tarah oont kaat'taa hai? phir aap ney usey batil qarar diya, yani uskey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya."
4986,"Hazrat Yaala ibn Muniyah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Tameem key eik aadmi ney eik dusrey shakhs sey ladaai ki aur uskey haath par daant gaad diye. us ney apna haath khincha to sath hi us ka daant bhi bahar aa gaya. wo ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey to aap ney farmaya : tum apney bhai ko is tarah kaat'tey ho jis tarah oont kaat'taa hai? phir aap ney usey batil qarar diya, yani uskey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya."
4987,"Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) key beton Hazrat Salma aur Yaala Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey. hamarey sath hamara eik sathi bhi tha. wo kisi dusrey musalman sey lad pada. us aadmi ney uskey bazu par daant gaad diye. us ney bazu uskey munh sey khincha to sath daant bhi nikal aaya. wo aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur diyat dilwaney ka mutalba karney laga. aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai ko ja kar is tarah kaat'taa hai jaisey oont chabaataa hai. phir aa kar diyat maangna shuru kar deta hai? is (tarah key daanton) ki koi diyat nahin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey daant ka koi moawza na dilwaya."
